        <processinfo id="ref55">
            <head>Processing Information Note</head>
            <p>Materials in this collection had previously been artificially separated into two collections: Drawings and Papers. During processing, materials were integrated into one collection, due to the material's content and nature of the original donation. Materials have been rehoused in acid-free folders and boxes. Because of the variety of formats and sizes found in the collection, intellectual arrangement does not reflect physical arrangement in all instances. Select items have received conservation treatment.</p>
        </processinfo>
